thread.title_full: BRIEF-cBrain signs deal with National Board of Social Services to deliver F2 | Reuters

author: Reuters
title: BRIEF-cBrain signs deal with National Board of Social Services to deliver F2
text:
Oct 23 cBrain A/S :
* The National Board of Social Services has signed an agreement with cBrain
* Contract is for the supply of F2 case and document management system based on the new national purchase framework for cloud services SKI 02.19 Cloud
